reviewText:
Alright, so i will not rate this game more so because i honestly believe the idea is GREAT.  Seriously i felt like it was real but the graphics, the mechanics and some issues are what is seriously hampering the games progress.  I recommend a revamp on the game to build it up for an official release.

To the creator/team;
You guys are great for putting forth a game that not many people could make.  Just my advice being an avid gamer is try to not rush things.  You can see that games like GTA V and other big titles are taking their time either because of competition or because they feel they can fix things for a great release.  You are on the right track and i hope to expect more from you all.
